<div id="hcalendar-2012-30-14T19:30" class="vevent"><abbr title="2012-30-14T19:30" class="dtstart">Tuesday 14, 19:30 </abbr><a href="http://juanroyo.blogspot.com/2012/02/ciclo-de-comic-en-ibercaja.html" class="url"> <span class= "summary">Victor Romano, taller. El mundo del fanzine y de la autoedición </span> <span class= "location">Lugar: Ibercaja </span></a>
